| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2132 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8296a42e-1ceb-5d10-b4c5-2b88c7830f78"
